      "text": "<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-left-style:solid !important;border-left-width:1px !important;border-right-color:!important;border-right-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">1</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">Een groep 16-jarigen staat in een zaaltje fanatiek te dansen.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-left-style:solid !important;border-left-width:1px !important;border-right-color:!important;border-right-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">2</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">Bibliotheken in Nederland hebben het moeilijk: het afgelopen decennium verdwenen er 140.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-left-style:solid !important;border-left-width:1px !important;border-right-color:!important;border-right-style:none;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">3</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">De Raad van Cultuur, die vandaag met een advies over bibliotheken komt voor het ministerie van OCW, vindt die ontwikkeling zorgelijk.</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-left-style:solid !important;border-left-width: